com.safenetinc.luna

Enum UserRole

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<UserRole>
      • com.safenetinc.luna.UserRole
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<UserRole>

    public enum UserRole
extends java.lang.Enum<UserRole>
    Enumerates the roles that a user can log in to a token with. Each role is associated with a specific PKCS11 user type. USER and CRYPTO_OFFICER are the same PKCS role, as are LIMITED_USER and CRYPTO_USER.
